              data-te-ripple-color="light"
              href="/contact"
              role="button">Enquire Now</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div
          class="justify-center items-center flex-1 max-w-screen-2xl px-6 p-6 mx-auto font-poppins"
        >
          <!-- About block 1 -->
          <div class="mb-16 flex flex-wrap">
            <div
              class="mb-6 w-full shrink-0 grow-0 basis-auto lg:mb-0 lg:w-6/12 lg:pr-6"
            >
              <div
                class="ripple relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-cover bg-[50%] bg-no-repeat shadow-lg"
                data-te-ripple-init
                data-te-ripple-color="light"
              >
                <img src="h3.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Louvre" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="w-full my-auto mx-auto shrink-0 grow-0 basis-auto lg:w-6/12 lg:pl-6"
            >
              <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-800">
                We represent farms in California, US to facilitate quality
                produce straight from the farm to your fork.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-800">
                We source English Walnuts of Chandler, Tulare and Howard
                varieties from farms that have been cared for the past 25 years
                and boast of a rich legacy of cultivating the fruits
                scientifically.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- About block 2 -->
          <div class="mb-16 flex flex-wrap lg:flex-row-reverse">
            <div
              class="mb-6 w-full shrink-0 grow-0 basis-auto lg:mb-0 lg:w-6/12 lg:pl-6"
            >
              <div
                class="ripple relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-cover bg-[50%] bg-no-repeat shadow-lg"
                data-te-ripple-init
                data-te-ripple-color="light"
              >
                <img src="h4.jpg" class="w-full" alt="Louvre" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="w-full my-auto mx-auto shrink-0 grow-0 basis-auto lg:w-6/12 lg:pr-6"
            >
              <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-800">
                Our suppliers believe in the power of nature to inspire, heal,
                and teach. Our walnut orchards are not just a place to harvest
                nuts but where stories whisper through rustling leaves, where
                the seasons paint a canvas of wonder, and where the very essence
                of life is celebrated. The farms practice sustainable farming
                methods, respecting the land that nurtures us and ensuring that
                our orchards remains a thriving ecosystem for generations to
                come.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

